Ensure frequency is set to *Monthly* and units is set to *Thousands of Persons, Seasonally Adjusted*.&#x20;

In the event FRED stops timely reporting the data, Admins may name a different resolution source if they deem the methodology is substantially the same. (For example, the December 2024 result would need to be approximately 3,012 thousand or 3.012 million.) In the event it is deemed impossible to find a comparable source, this question may be **annulled**.

Please note that as of April 2025 the FRED source reports the figure in "Thousands of Persons" and this question is similarly in units of thousands of people.
